{"about_the_game":"Play as a witch\u2019s canine familiar tasked with saving magical creatures and solving a mystery. <br>Herdles walks the line between an epic adventure and a puzzle platformer, using barking as the main mechanic of the game. <br><br>Explore a dynamic environment of lush hills and forests that get increasingly more magical as the game progresses. <br>There is no combat or death, instead you are offered multiple humorous and puzzly solutions to deal with adversaries in the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Bark Changes Everything</strong></h2>Everything reacts to your bark. Reveal secrets, trigger mechanisms, and explore an interactive world full of magic and wonder!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429600/extras/20240627_herdles_barkAtEverything.gif?t=1724100449\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>All Roads Lead To Home</strong></h2>There are multiple ways to progress through the world. Experiment and think out of the box to find the most efficient and/or funniest solutions to any obstacle you might face.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429600/extras/road.gif?t=1724100449\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>No Hurdles, Just Herdles</strong></h2>Herdles has a strong focus on modern accessibility and offers settings to accommodate people with various disabilities, but also includes a variety of options that change the game itself. Tune the game to your needs/preferences and play it as a challenging parkour with lots of dangers or as a cozy experience without conflict.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429600/extras/herdles20230917_002_steamaccessibility.gif?t=1724100449\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724100449","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steams